    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can add half your Proficiency Bonus, rounded down, to any ability check you make with a tool that does not already include your Proficiency Bonus.</p><p>You also learn how to produce exactly the tool you need: with Thieves' Tools or Artisan's Tools, you can magically create one set of Artisan's Tools in an unoccupied space within 5 feet of you. This creation requires 1 hour of uninterrupted work, which can coincide with a Short or Long Rest. Though the product of magic, the tools are nonmagical, and they vanish when you use this feature again.</p>",
